  m_text: "\n\n\nDay 1 \u2013 Field Log\nArrived at the cave entrance at 0600 hours.
    Initial scans confirm unusual seismic readings originating from within. Command
    wants all available data retrieved and logged.\L\nThe interior is deeper than
    expected. Some interference in our instruments, cause unknown.\L\nProceeding
    further inside."
